c: 6
v: 65
t: "Nena, “Iye ali ndi mphamvu yotumiza chilango chake pa inu kuchokerapamutupanukapenapansipamapazianukapena kukugawani inu kukhala m’magulu a anthu osagwirizana ndi kukulawitsani mazunzo ochokera kwa anzanu. Taonani mmene timaonetsera poyera chivumbulutso chathu kuti akhale ozindikira.”"